  "The most translated film library in the world": "全球翻譯最多的電影資料庫",
  "Decades of translation work, carried by trusted ministry partners, have built a library with thousands of language tracks so people can encounter the story of Jesus in the language that reaches them deepest.": "數十年來，由可信賴的事工合作夥伴所進行的翻譯工作，建立了一個擁有數千種語言的資料庫，讓人們可以用最深入他們的語言來認識耶穌的故事。",
  "Carrying trusted voices into new formats": "將值得信賴的聲音轉換成新的形式",
  "We are rebuilding how gospel stories are told visually, pairing trusted translations with modern formats so the message can move freely across platforms, cultures, and screen.": "我們正在重建福音故事的視覺傳播方式，將值得信賴的譯本與現代格式結合，讓訊息可以自由地跨平台、跨文化、跨螢幕傳播。",
  "More than a library. A mission-driven team.": "不只是圖書館。一個以使命為導向的團隊。",
  "Jesus Film Project is a global team of translators, media specialists, editors, and creators who have served missionaries for decades. We're turning that experience into tools that equip disciple-makers everywhere.": "耶穌電影計畫是一個由翻譯、媒體專家、編輯和創作人所組成的全球性團隊，他們為宣教士服務已有數十年之久。我們將經驗轉化為工具，裝備各地的門徒訓練者。",
  "Next Steps Platform": "下一步平台",
  "Connect every viewer with tangible opportunities on their spiritual journey, helping them take a next step into community, Scripture, or mission.": "將每一位觀眾與他們靈修之旅的實質機會聯繫起來，幫助他們在社群、經文或宣教方面踏出下一步。",
  "Evangelistic Media Library": "佈道媒體圖書館",
  "We have an extensive Christian media library with thousands of videos, films, and resources available in multiple languages for ministry and evangelism worldwide.": "我們擁有龐大的基督教媒體圖書館，以多種語言提供數以千計的影片、電影和資源，供全球事工和傳福音之用。",
  "Digital Tools for Ministries": "事工數位工具",
  "Comprehensive digital tools designed specifically for ministry needs, including video management, content distribution, audience engagement, and analytics to help ministries reach more people effectively.": "專為事工需求設計的全面數位工具，包括視訊管理、內容發行、觀眾參與及分析，協助事工有效接觸更多人。",
  "Built for global missions": "專為全球任務打造",
  "The message doesn't change. The way people watch does.": "訊息不會改變。人們觀看的方式會改變。",
  "We are rebuilding our video library and tools from the ground up, committing decades of translation work to the platforms where people already gather, watch, and share.": "我們正在從頭開始重建我們的視訊資料庫和工具，將數十年來的翻譯工作投入到人們已經聚集、觀看和分享的平台上。",
  "What we are building next": "我們下一步的建設",
  "You're invited": "我們邀請您",
  "Help build <2>the next generation</2> of mission tools": "協助建立<2>下一代</2>的任務工具",
